    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "The main business objective of this analysis is to understand the key factors that influence Airbnb listing performance in New York City. By analyzing pricing trends, room types, neighbourhood popularity, and customer reviews, this project aims to provide actionable insights that can help hosts optimize their pricing strategies and improve listing attractiveness.\n",
        "\n",
        "Additionally, the analysis can help Airbnb identify high-demand areas, understand customer behavior, and support better decision-making for marketing strategies, property recommendations, and host guidance to increase booking rates and overall platform growth."
