        "### Variables Description"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "PBTbrJXOngz2"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "The dataset contains Airbnb listing information for New York City. Each row represents a unique listing available on the Airbnb platform.\n",
        "\n",
        "The dataset contains the following important variables:\n",
        "\n",
        "• **id** – Unique identifier for each listing\n",
        "• **name** – Name or title of the Airbnb listing\n",
        "• **host_id** – Unique identifier for the host\n",
        "• **host_name** – Name of the host managing the listing\n",
        "• **neighbourhood_group** – Broad geographical area (Manhattan, Brooklyn, Queens, Bronx, Staten Island)\n",
        "• **neighbourhood** – Specific neighborhood within the group\n",
        "• **latitude & longitude** – Geographic coordinates of the listing\n",
        "• **room_type** – Type of property offered (Entire home, Private room, Shared room)\n",
        "• **price** – Cost of renting the listing per night\n",
        "• **minimum_nights** – Minimum number of nights required to book the listing\n",
        "• **number_of_reviews** – Total number of reviews received\n",
        "• **last_review** – Date of the most recent review\n",
        "• **reviews_per_month** – Average number of reviews per month\n",
        "• **calculated_host_listings_count** – Total listings managed by the host\n",
        "• **availability_365** – Number of days the listing is available in a year\n",
        "\n",
        "These variables help analyze pricing trends, listing availability, host activity, and customer engagement patterns across different neighborhoods.\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "aJV4KIxSnxay"
      }
    },
